{"tid":1280664,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"各位重讀緊書嘅同我全部入哂黎","createTime":"2019-07-03T05:01:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T01:58:02.000Z","uid":18577,"like":614,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"215d0830d0667de8ed25b608694f311ccd87293a","tid":1280664,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T05:01:56.000Z","msg":"今次讀書真係重讀緊書嘅年輕人佔多數<br />\n你地咁關心香港都係因為你地留意時事..有獨立分析..所以明白到依家香港係處於水深火熱當中<br />\n<br />\n我係道請大家一定要用出黎抗爭既耐性同精神去好好讀書..考返一個對得住自己對得住香港既好成績<br />\n<br />\n到時入到大學..然後係各界專業人士上面都會見到你地..運用你地嘅知識社會地位黎一齊對抗依個政府<br />\n<br />\n我真係好希望能夠黎緊當記者訪問今屆狀元嘅時候<br />\n大家可以狠狠打政府一巴..等佢地知道依班年輕人既諗法"},{"pid":"b075d798116209973cba9b93a722001f131dfd2e","tid":1280664,"uid":18577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T05:03:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"051972376f8425bc7452b7933c9424140ec21f67","tid":1280664,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T05:04:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"84be62cac26c065b6130af22919c44b71cc9f236","tid":1280664,"uid":36478,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T05:05:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"968c4af12828f33ae639fb2f9663249b35362f83","tid":1280664,"uid":154054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T05:05:47.000Z","msg":"堆"},{"pid":"39203dd6875b300e66c74263fea3cfc605f81df7","tid":1280664,"uid":18577,"like":52,"dislike":2,"score":50,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T05:07:22.000Z","msg":"一定要出盡力努力讀書考好成績<br />\n依樣都係你能夠為香港做嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02e01bf6cd82cf19d7d98559f347d501a25c5360","tid":1280664,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T05:10:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"62cdf2b3b399a58910c1049f2a3ed60d1d87bfe0","tid":1280664,"uid":242889,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T05:12:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ff3ef